S.FORM: Dan Amboyer kawas tay 1985, ryax sa tay 28 nqu tay 12, Dan Amboyer, squliq na Bunge'. Dan Amboyer ,Claudi ru Donald Amboyer msqun hintgan maki Detroit. raral ga,hiya mqwas beh Roeper ru Interlochen pqwasan biru.suruw lga hiya tmasoq biru maki Carnegie Mellon pqwasan.tmasoq mqwas lga,musa maki Nork York. Amboyer mhtuw maki cingay TV ru ega'. hiya ga tequtux squilq maki Theatre kosi Exit. 2017 kawas 10 byacing 7 ryax skayal tnaq mlikuy (Eric P.Berger) msqun la. soni hngan qani ga,cyux tktan kwara mhtuw Access Hollywood E telivi. 2019 kawas 11 byacing 4 ryax,hiya skayal nya mha cyux kian Berger la maki Instagram. hiya laqi mlikuy(Theodore Carl Amboyer Berger) nya hintgan 2019 kawas 12 byacing 23 ryax.
